38:23.791 --> 38:26.250
[grunts] Dorothy...

38:28.458 --> 38:30.083
-[video game beeping]
-Dorothy...

38:38.333 --> 38:39.375
[whimpers]

38:42.250 --> 38:44.458
[breathing heavily, shivering]

38:46.375 --> 38:48.625
[whimpering]

38:49.583 --> 38:50.750
Dorothy!

38:52.166 --> 38:53.500
Papa?

38:53.583 --> 38:56.333
Come to me, darling.
But first...

38:56.416 --> 38:59.041
-you must cover your eyes.
-What?

38:59.125 --> 39:00.250
Why?

39:00.333 --> 39:02.416
Just do as a I say, please.

39:02.500 --> 39:04.916
-[ominous music playing]
-[Dorothy] No...

39:05.291 --> 39:06.916
[crying]

39:07.000 --> 39:10.000
[Niles] Dorothy, don't look.

39:10.083 --> 39:11.750
Close your eyes.

39:15.541 --> 39:17.208
I did this.

39:17.291 --> 39:19.625
This is all on me.

39:22.291 --> 39:23.375
Cliff.

39:24.458 --> 39:26.416
[whimpering, yelling]

39:26.500 --> 39:30.458
It'll be all right, darling.
We can still fix this.

39:30.541 --> 39:32.833
[intense music playing]

39:37.625 --> 39:40.916
[grunts, coughing]

39:41.000 --> 39:43.458
Dorothy, please.

39:44.625 --> 39:46.291
Darling...

39:47.166 --> 39:48.666
come to me.

39:51.583 --> 39:53.416
[woman] No.

39:53.500 --> 39:54.750
[coughs]

39:55.958 --> 39:57.166
Slava.

40:12.000 --> 40:13.916
You cannot wait
any longer, child.

40:14.000 --> 40:16.666
-Don't listen to her.
-He can't protect you.

40:16.750 --> 40:18.208
Neither can your friends.

40:21.125 --> 40:22.541
It is up to you...

40:23.333 --> 40:24.666
alone.

40:29.125 --> 40:30.583
[electricity crackling]

41:01.041 --> 41:02.750
She's not here.

41:03.791 --> 41:05.250
I know.

41:05.666 --> 41:07.666
How dare you!

41:07.750 --> 41:11.000
You unleashed this thing
on your own daughter!

41:11.083 --> 41:14.291
Are you a little girl?
Or are you a woman?

41:19.916 --> 41:22.333
[eerie music plays]

41:22.416 --> 41:24.333
[muffled yelling]

41:24.416 --> 41:26.083
[Niles]<i> She will always be</i>
<i>a little girl.</i>

41:26.166 --> 41:28.250
-She has to be!
-You don't know.

41:28.333 --> 41:29.750
I know that

41:29.833 --> 41:32.041
she cannot beat him!

41:32.125 --> 41:35.250
You're not Miranda, are you?

41:37.416 --> 41:38.958
[Slava]<i> It is her time.</i>

41:41.083 --> 41:42.416
And she must grow up.

41:45.000 --> 41:46.541
Then who are you?

41:47.000 --> 41:48.333
Oh...

41:50.291 --> 41:52.000
Sweet baby.

41:54.000 --> 41:56.375
Don't do it. Don't you do it!

41:57.875 --> 41:59.375
Listen to me.

41:59.458 --> 42:02.875
You can't beat him.
Look at the others.

42:02.958 --> 42:04.625
Look at how
he destroyed them.

42:04.708 --> 42:07.708
What chance does
a little girl have?

42:07.791 --> 42:09.625
Don't do this, Dorothy,

42:09.708 --> 42:11.208
I'm begging you.

42:12.541 --> 42:14.083
It's all right, Papa.

42:15.125 --> 42:16.875
I know what I have to do now.

42:46.708 --> 42:48.375
[Slava] Girl...

42:50.250 --> 42:51.875
you need a weapon.

42:54.500 --> 42:55.833
I can make my own.

42:55.916 --> 42:57.833
[upbeat music playing]

43:22.416 --> 43:24.708
Dorothy...

43:24.791 --> 43:27.750
[in Candlemaker's voice]
Come, girl, and meet your fate.

43:34.541 --> 43:37.208
[shouting] Dorothy!

43:41.166 --> 43:42.875
[sobbing]
